trans-unit.source: Forms the basis for the strongly typed collections that are members of the <see cref="N:System.Web.Services.Description" /> namespace.
An object for which to return the name of the key.
Returns the name of the key associated with the value passed by reference.
A null reference.
The default implementation of this method is intended to be overridden by a derived class in order to return the name of the key associated with the `value` parameter.
trans-unit.target: 此方法的默认实现旨在为派生类重写，以便返回与关联的密钥的名称`value`参数。

trans-unit.source: The default implementation returns null (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: 默认实现返回 null (`Nothing`在 Visual Basic 中)。

trans-unit.source: This protected method is accessible only through this class or a derived class.

Sets the parent object of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionBaseCollection" /> instance.
